  "texts": [
    "The HP concerns why and how physical processes in the brain give rise to subjective experiences.",
    "It's about understanding why certain brain functions are accompanied by an experience of 'what it is like' -the qualitative, experiential, or phenomenological aspects of consciousness.",
    "The HP delves into the nature of consciousness itself, asking why cognitive processing is accompanied by subjective experience.",
    "The SGP is primarily a problem of representation and understanding in artificial systems: how a symbol (or word) can be meaningfully connected to what it represents.",
    "The HP, on the other hand, is more profound and addresses the very nature of consciousness and experience."
